<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="roundabout-adj">roundabout <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'raʊndəbaʊt/    美 /'raʊndəbaʊt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>迂回的；不直截了当的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>take a roundabout route 
绕道</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You speak in a <strong>roundabout way</strong>. 
你说话拐弯抹角。</p></div></div>